  "content": "<p data-pid=\"ykuEurLQ\">本系列专门介绍 SuperMemo 的各种小技巧和绕坑方法：</p><a href=\"https://www.zhihu.com/collection/797904700\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" class=\"internal\">SuperMemo tips</a><p data-pid=\"YT86A9-Q\">以下内容来自：</p><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.yuque.com/supermemo/faq/fa6y6q\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic2.zhimg.com/v2-4138b37229a0a7128e306a875f5ddc65_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1266\" data-image-height=\"952\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">SuperMemo 摘录会回到文章开头 · 语雀</a><hr/><h2>问题描述</h2><p data-pid=\"l3Rom9IY\">对于一些长文，摘录一段话后，SuperMemo 会让光标跳到开头，严重影响阅读。</p><h2>解决方案</h2><h3>方案一</h3><p data-pid=\"r1_W8rqS\">Ctrl+Shift+F12，去除文章中的所有样式（包括图片），然后再摘录就不会乱跳了。</p><h3>方案二</h3><p data-pid=\"yIFVke3P\">用 split 功能将文章分割成多份。</p><p data-pid=\"EDGzsJHm\">首先，先右键点击文本，找到分割文章功能：</p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4138b37229a0a7128e306a875f5ddc65_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1266\" data-rawheight=\"952\" data-original-token=\"v2-4138b37229a0a7128e306a875f5ddc65\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5ec806a9069094d674d1b219b9f1d7b1_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1266\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4138b37229a0a7128e306a875f5ddc65_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1266&#39; height=&#39;952&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1266\" data-rawheight=\"952\" data-original-token=\"v2-4138b37229a0a7128e306a875f5ddc65\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-5ec806a9069094d674d1b219b9f1d7b1_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1266\" data-original=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-4138b37229a0a7128e306a875f5ddc65_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-4138b37229a0a7128e306a875f5ddc65_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"xpm_tXx0\"><br/>然后，勾选 Custom string（自带的分割标签可能会出问题）<br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d11f87e73da696de22745e1e2fa11b8b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1604\" data-rawheight=\"668\" data-original-token=\"v2-d11f87e73da696de22745e1e2fa11b8b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3a87d175c9e9401029a3cc51c5425a90_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1604\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d11f87e73da696de22745e1e2fa11b8b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1604&#39; height=&#39;668&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1604\" data-rawheight=\"668\" data-original-token=\"v2-d11f87e73da696de22745e1e2fa11b8b\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/50/v2-3a87d175c9e9401029a3cc51c5425a90_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1604\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-d11f87e73da696de22745e1e2fa11b8b_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/50/v2-d11f87e73da696de22745e1e2fa11b8b_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"yteZqWxp\">然后，输入<code>&lt;h</code>，点击确定，就可以把这篇文章按照各级标题分割了。<br/></p><figure data-size=\"normal\"><noscript><img src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c3cd6051f847354bffa860c2275319c2_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1366\" data-rawheight=\"658\" data-original-token=\"v2-c3cd6051f847354bffa860c2275319c2\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-06202543c7f8bc3dce52bf664a9491cd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb\" width=\"1366\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c3cd6051f847354bffa860c2275319c2_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></noscript><img src=\"data:image/svg+xml;utf8,&lt;svg xmlns=&#39;http://www.w3.org/2000/svg&#39; width=&#39;1366&#39; height=&#39;658&#39;&gt;&lt;/svg&gt;\" data-caption=\"\" data-size=\"normal\" data-rawwidth=\"1366\" data-rawheight=\"658\" data-original-token=\"v2-c3cd6051f847354bffa860c2275319c2\" data-default-watermark-src=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-06202543c7f8bc3dce52bf664a9491cd_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\" class=\"origin_image zh-lightbox-thumb lazy\" width=\"1366\" data-original=\"https://picx.zhimg.com/v2-c3cd6051f847354bffa860c2275319c2_r.jpg?source=2c26e567\" data-actualsrc=\"https://pica.zhimg.com/50/v2-c3cd6051f847354bffa860c2275319c2_720w.jpg?source=2c26e567\"/></figure><p data-pid=\"zTNIMN4X\">分割后的文章片段，SuperMemo 会安排在未来几天进行阅读。由于篇幅变短，出现乱转跳 bug 的概率也会变低。</p><hr/><p data-pid=\"DiPZNIUO\">更多 SuperMemo 教程，请见：</p><a href=\"https://zhuanlan.zhihu.com/p/374403541\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-1a8d0bb90f07e4147c5e401dda14d280_180x120.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1780\" data-image-height=\"1100\" class=\"internal\">叶峻峣：渐进学习专栏导读</a><a href=\"https://link.zhihu.com/?target=https%3A//www.yuque.com/supermemo/wiki/help\" data-draft-node=\"block\" data-draft-type=\"link-card\" data-image=\"https://pic1.zhimg.com/v2-b97a11638b50bbc6500138df61b728f4_ipico.jpg\" data-image-width=\"1000\" data-image-height=\"1000\" class=\" wrap external\" target=\"_blank\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\">SuperMemo 18帮助文档 · 语雀</a><p></p>",
